   "type": "text",
   "x": 40,
   "y": 398,
   "width": 1791.03,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "The controller runs the same audit, onboard, stage, verify, and retire playbooks by hand or through Semaphore, both pointed at one Git project. Audit only reads state; retirement runs only after a staged key, clean prechecks, the verified flag, and an exact confirmation phrase all pass.",
   "originalText": "The controller runs the same audit, onboard, stage, verify, and retire playbooks by hand or through Semaphore, both pointed at one Git project. Audit only reads state; retirement runs only after a staged key, clean prechecks, the verified flag, and an exact confirmation phrase all pass.",
